author: NEW YORK DAILY NEWS
title: Kendall Jenner's new H&M commericial
text:
She’s going to work by going to twerk.
Kendall Jenner shows off her dancing skills in a new campaign for The Balmain X H&M Collection .
In a video for the fashion campaign, the 19-year-old reality TV star-turned-model is seen twerking with dancers and other models.
Her friend and fellow modeling sensation, Gigi Hadid, is also part of the “Balmain Gang.”
Yahoo Kendall Jenner behind the scenes of the new Balmain for H&M campaign. The video, directed by Johan Sandberg and Henrik Timonen, also stars Balmain's creative director, Olivier Rousteing.
"Kendall had a lot of fun. The campaign has to reflect the Balmain Army and for me, she is the most important," Rousteing told Yahoo .
"She is an icon. I'm inspired by her. For me she is the new Naomi (Campbell), Claudia (Schiffer), Cindy (Crawford).
Yahoo Kendall Jenner behind the scenes of the new H&M campaign. “You know the type of models where people want to be her. She also has an amazing soul and is so supportive."
The Balmain X H&M Collection is launching on Nov. 5, but there will be an exclusive runway show at 7:30 p.m. Tuesday that will stream live on Periscope.
